<P><BOLD>CANADA PROVINCE OF NOVA SCOTIA</BOLD></P>
<P>Grant Thornton Limited in its capacity as Trustee of the Bankrupt Estate and Administrator of the Consumer Proposal of Joseph Edward Hendsbee (&ldquo;Hendsbee&rdquo;) hereby applies to the Registrar of the Supreme Court of Nova Scotia as follows:
