<P1>2. In the alternative, a Discharge Order for Hendsbee pursuant to Section <EM>172.1(6) BIA</EM>, modifying the Conditional Order of Discharge issued by this Honourable Court on October 1, 2005.</P1></P>
<P>Attached is the Affidavit of Daniel Rozon dated April 1st, 2014 in support of this application.</P>
